`8Keywords``   : Cleanse
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast 'cleanse' <target>

 Cleanse uses magical energies to drive out harmful diseases and curses from
the body of the spell's target.  This is a power that priests are eventually
trained in.

